'''Horus-Re''', ({{Pronounce|HOR|us|RAY|refs=}}) known as '''Helcaliant''' in [[Thay]] and '''Hokatep''' in [[Unther]], was the leader of the [[Mulhorandi pantheon]]. Once the change-promoting deity simply known as '''Horus''', the young god received the powers and personality of his slain father [[Re]], becoming a more staunch traditionalist.
